data.eml:eml: Thalassironus filiformis sp. nov. (Nematoda, Enoplida) from the South China Sea

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Huang, Mian, Huang, Yong, Xu, Kuidong (2019): Thalassironus filiformis sp. nov. (Nematoda, Enoplida) from the South China Sea. Zootaxa 4657 (1): 170-176, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4657.1.8
